Author: zneww
Title: ICON - ICO in 23 hours ...
Body: Very important news!  1. ID Editing Policy  Allow usage of Photoshop or other computer programs to hide the unique identification number      Before: Modification with Photoshop or other computer programs NOT ALLOWED     After: Modification with Photoshop, Paint, and other computer programs ALLOWED  ※ In principle, we have requested to cover the unique identification number using paper, “Post-it”, or finger in order to prevent the risk of counterfeit/alteration. However, to reflect the suggestion from the contributors, we have decided that simply erasing the unique identification number with Photoshop or other computer programs will not have a great influence on the validity of the original ID. We will always do our best to accommodate the opinions of ICON contributors within our principles.

Author: DutchFinity
Title: ICON - ICO in 23 hours ...
Body: First of all; I don't think that the developers come here. At least I have not been spotting them. I did encounter them on Telegram.  Now about your tokens. They have already been sent to your wallet. Did you pay with myetherwallet? I hope you bought your tokens with an ERC20 wallet. Well suppose you used myetherwallet. You need to add the ICX token. For this you click 'Ad Custom Token'. Then you fill in:  address : 0xb5A5F22694352C15B00323844aD545ABb2B11028 symbol : ICX decimals : 18  Now your ICX will show.  At the moment your ICX's however are still locked. To unlock them you need to follow the KYC procedure. That procedure will start on 2 October. If all is well they will email you (I suppose). So untill the 2nd of October we don't need to, and can't, do much with our tokens.  Good that you bought for almost an entire ETH. I had less to spend.
